Step 1: install Qt-creator (if not already installed)

$sudo apt-get install qtcreator

Step 2: cd into catkin_ws/src


Step 3: ls-l 


Step 4:  Replace existing CMakelist.txt with /opt/ros/indigo/share/catkin/cmake/toplevel.cmake
$cp /opt/ros/indigo/share/catkin/cmake/toplevel.cmake CMakelist.txt

step 5: Open Qtcreator from terminal

step 6: click open project and choose the CMakelist.txt found in catkin_ws/src

Step 7: set build dir to already existing build path - being catkin_ws/build

Step 8 : Done - Celebrate !!


